### Read all users
GET http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users

### Create a new user
POST http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"Charlie",
    "email": "charlie@example.com",
    "password": "pass1234"
}

### Update a user
PUT http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"Sign2",
    "email": "wathisa@example.com",
    "password": "pass123"
}

### Delete a user 
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/v2/users/1